description:
Hayden returns looking awesome! I figured I would put some tatted up guys together, and Shiloh, though in his personal life tends to be a Top, is on Bottom again.
He is pretty versatile, but Hayden was more in the zone to top, so we had him take the lead. That really doesn't stop Shiloh from taking charge, guiding experienced Hayden though some major ass fucking!
title: Hayden & Shiloh - RAW
